How to install Helm on CentOS 7?

Step 1:  wget https://get.helm.sh/helm-v3.5.4-linux-amd64.tar.gz

Step 2: tar -zxvf helm-v3.5.4-linux-amd64.tar.gz

Step 3: sudo mv linux-amd64/helm /usr/local/bin/helm

Step 4: helm version
